cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image completion using lexical semantics, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) domains. The paper also proposes a model that uses multi-grained reasoning blocks and a multi-stage training strategy, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses potential applications in art and design, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) category.
